#. (itstool) path: listitem/para
#: article.translate.xml:415
msgid "your kernel configuration (including which hardware devices you have installed)"
msgstr ""

#. (itstool) path: listitem/para
#: article.translate.xml:420
msgid "whether or not you have debugging options enabled (such as <literal>WITNESS</literal>), and if so, whether the problem persists when you change the sense of that option"
