#. (itstool) path: listitem/para
#: article.translate.xml:448
msgid "whether or not you can run any other kernel as a fallback (this is to rule out hardware-related issues such as failing disks and overheating CPUs, which can masquerade as kernel problems)"
msgstr ""

#. (itstool) path: listitem/para
#: article.translate.xml:457
msgid "If this is a ports problem, then be prepared to supply the following information. (You do not have to include these by default, which only tends to fill up the database, but you should include excerpts that you think might be relevant):"
