#. (itstool) path: listitem/para
#: article.translate.xml:519
msgid "<emphasis>Avoid controversial requests.</emphasis> If your PR addresses an area that has been controversial in the past, you should probably be prepared to not only offer patches, but also justification for why the patches are <quote>The Right Thing To Do</quote>. As noted above, a careful search of the mailing lists using the archives at <uri xlink:href=\"https://www.FreeBSD.org/search/search.html#mailinglists\">https://www.FreeBSD.org/search/search.html#mailinglists</uri> is always good preparation."
